         UPDATED=20221122
           SHORT="Some commandline utilities relating to inotify"

cat << EOF
inotify-tools is a C library and a set of command-line programs for
Linux providing a simple interface to inotify. These programs can be
used to monitor and act upon filesystem events.
The general purpose of this package is to allow inotify's features to
be used from within shell scripts.
EOF
